### Create subscription
POST http://localhost:8080/api/subscriptions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startDate": "2025-01-01",
  "status": "Ativo",
  "paymentMethod": "Pix",
  "planId": 1,
  "studentId": 1
}

###

### List all subscriptions
GET http://localhost:8080/api/subscriptions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Filter by student name
GET http://localhost:8080/api/subscriptions?studentName=João
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get subscription by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/subscriptions/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Update subscription
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/subscriptions/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startDate": "2025-02-01",
  "status": "Ativo",
  "paymentMethod": "Cartão",
  "planId": 1,
  "studentId": 1
}

###

### Delete subscription
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/subscriptions/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
